{"tid":24642,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[基夫修打蘭] 指定倖存者 Designated Survivor 第一季","createTime":"2016-12-05T15:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T07:56:53.000Z","uid":32934,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6c16c884dd176a7c7ca4c9e79ee6bd210d6a9127","tid":24642,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:54:47.000Z","msg":"舊POST:<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum12.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=VI&amp;message=6599700\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum12.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DVI%26message%3D6599700&d=jrWVSpMJYTM9%2F%2BTkK0Hr33vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=54b26ac7\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum12.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=VI&amp;message=6599700</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://images6.fanpop.com/image/photos/39600000/-Designated-Survivor-Key-Art-designated-survivor-39619235-1898-1068.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages6.fanpop.com%2Fimage%2Fphotos%2F39600000%2F-Designated-Survivor-Key-Art-designated-survivor-39619235-1898-1068.jpg&h=9710d77a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nKiefer Sutherland 不再做24小時唔飲水食野去廁所既反恐英雄，直接坐上總統寶座？呢套新劇係佢飾演美國政府住屋及城市發展部長Tom Kirkman。故事開頭美國總統及各政府高官齊集國會，發表國情咨文。但按照慣例，有一名高官會不參與此事，並擔當指定生還者，倘若全體官員遇難時便會馬上就任總統，以維持國家運作。不幸既事情亦就此發生了！國會大爆炸，全體人員無一生還！本來在當日早上，總統仲有意炒佢，但此刻竟然做埋總統！國難在前，幕僚亦不相信佢可以擔任總統之位，另謀對策。到底Tom會點樣令大家信服，帶領國家？同時Maggie Q飾演既FBI探員係爆炸現場調查，發現此爆炸並非一般恐佈襲擊，似乎另有內情，到底真相如何？此劇開首開得唔錯，有追看性！在此推薦此劇，一齊睇一齊討論！<br />\n<br />\nTrailer:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N_f1v0Nx5Sw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DN_f1v0Nx5Sw&d=jrWVSpMJYTM9%2F%2BTkK0Hr33vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=513d6b9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N_f1v0Nx5Sw</a><br />\n<br />\nSEED<br />\n<a href=\"https://rarbg.to/torrents.php?category=1;18;41\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frarbg.to%2Ftorrents.php%3Fcategory%3D1%3B18%3B41&d=jrWVSpMJYTM9%2F%2BTkK0Hr33vM